    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables are starting to caramelise, remove the pan from the heat, then add your <strong>udon noodles</strong> and <strong>spinach </strong>with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong></p><p>Return the pan to the heat and cook, covered for 2 min or until the spinach has started to wilt</p><p>Tip: Gently separate the noodles with a fork!</p>",
