    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the spinach has wilted, add the <strong>peanut sauce</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up until the noodles are coated – this is your <strong>peanut butter veg-packed udon</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of water if the sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
